{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "黑衣少年驱逐满厅宾客，只留楚留香一人在室。楚留香依赌约问话，黑衣少年却狡黠地只允提问不允答复，二人言语交锋激烈，继而动武。黑衣少年的长鞭绝技飞环套月，行云布雨圈套连绵，楚留香以竹签投入鞭圈破之，机智绝伦。缠斗中楚留香发现有人暗器偷袭黑衣少年，暗中以分光捉影接下七星针。黑衣少年一鞭击中楚留香面颊得手，此时中原第一杀手一点红破窗而入，揭破楚留香为救黑衣少年而故意挨鞭的真相。黑衣少年深受感动，含泪留下那封神秘信件后离去。一点红却以剑挑信，逼楚留香与自己决斗。两人为争夺书信展开惊险绝伦的交手，最终楚留香以双掌夹住剑尖与书信，身子悬于剑上，二人僵持不下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚!全给我滚，一个也不许留在这里!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qiu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "冷秋魂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人全未惹着你，你何苦迁怒……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也快给我滚出去，快滚!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qiu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "冷秋魂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若不愿当着别人面前认输，我自然可以出去，只是……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qiu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "冷秋魂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是你要记住，这三鞭冷某总有一日要加倍奉还的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四鞭!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻人都已走了，阁下总可认输了吧?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要问什么?说吧!",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令尊入关前所接的那封书信，不知你是否瞧见过?不知那信上写着的究竟是什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知道我爹爹是谁?你怎知道他已入关?你又怎会知道他入关前曾经接着了一封书信?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫忘了，此刻是我在问你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你已问过了，现在是我在问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问的话，你尚未回答，又怎能问我?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只答应让你问我几句话，并未说一定要答复你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我总想瞧瞧世上最不讲理的人是谁，今日总算是瞧着了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你话已问过，玉璧不妨拿去，那姓冷的你也放他走了，你我赌约已践，现在，该你回答我问的话了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是我不回答呢?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死!",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是我不肯死呢?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不死，我死!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是我也不肯让你死呢?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好快的身法，好高的分光捉影。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你套圈圈还没有套够么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "永远套不够的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你要套到什么时候?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "套到你死为止。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "我若永远不死呢?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我就永远套下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "阁下的脾气，倒和牛相差无几。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若套得不耐烦，就赶快死吧!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "妙极妙极，这说法当真妙不可言，就连我……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你还想走?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "原来你早已约好了帮手。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "打输了就约帮手来，中原武林难道都是这样的人物?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你以为他败了?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "挨了一鞭子的，总不是我吧!",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你也想来他那一手么?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你瞧瞧再说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "若不是那挨了你一鞭子的人，你此刻还有命么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你说他是为了救我，才……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "他若不是为了要将这暗器击落，你连他衣角也休想沾着半点。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你方才为……为何不说?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "说不定这暗器并非要打你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "暗器自我身后击来，目标自然是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "挨你一鞭子，也没什么大不了，我又何苦说出来，让你难受。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "红兄，方才暗算的人，你可瞧见是谁么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我若瞧见，还会让他走?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "我也知道那人行动委实有如鬼魅一般，却再也猜不出他是谁，中原武林中，像他这样的高手其实并不多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道那是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你知道?是谁?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是你要看的信，拿去吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "多谢多谢。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "红兄这是在开玩笑么?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若要这封信，先胜过我这柄剑。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "我早已说过，不愿和你动手，你何苦逼我?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你能与那少年动手，为何不能与我动手?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "纵要动手，也等我瞧过信再说好么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "动手之后，我若死了，你自可将这封信取去，你若死了，我也必将这封信陪你殉葬。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "刚走了一个牛脾气，不想又来个比牛还拗的脾气。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    }
  ],
